title: (Mon Full Podcast) Gavin DeGraw Performs and Tells Stories Behind His Biggest Hits and Emotional Song from New Album + Rejected Segments! + Lunchbox Finally Has His Garage Sale
itunes:title: (Mon Full Podcast) Gavin DeGraw Performs and Tells Stories Behind His Biggest Hits and Emotional Song from New Album + Rejected Segments! + Lunchbox Finally Has His Garage Sale
description:
Gavin DeGraw stops by with his keyboard. He tells the story behind “I Don’t Wanna Be” and how it ended up as the theme song for One Tree Hill. He also shares the emotional story behind his new album and how it was dedicated to his late parents. Bobby shares a list of segments that have been rejected over the last month. Lunchbox had his big garage sale over the weekend and we found out how it went and how much money he made.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
